  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_0a4beced637aec718f15066786f5913b">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Under the Division of Financial Affairs, Cornell University's Policy Office coordinates the editing, review, issuance, and archiving of all official university policies. Standardized policies that have been through the official development process, and "legacy" policies that, in time, will be standardized.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_802add9cea04daf6513e00683989ec06">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>Digital files, including Cornell University policies and documented changes.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <accessrestrict audience="internal" id="aspace_b96eedcbbbefd2e30eb8a27384c51815">
    <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
