  <prefercite audience="internal" id="aspace_5c415ad4ebbf9c646f6ad6b577b64a6d">
    <head>Preferred Citation</head>
<p>Cornell University Policy Office records, #7-12-4421.  Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
  <processinfo audience="internal" id="aspace_576edf5e4dc90b69543cb66b7b5a6911">
    <head>Processing Information</head>
<p>The policy office managed policy documents dating 2005-2018 in a subversion repository. Archivist extracted every version of each file in "trunk" and renamed the file with the revision identifier prefixed to the original filename. The policy subversion log was also exported from the subversion repository and contains the revision identifier (column A), revision commit author using Cornell netID (column C), revision commit date (column D), revision commit message (column E) and original file name (column J).</p>  </processinfo>
  <relatedmaterial audience="internal" id="aspace_2eca5458418867f49fd661b033b65b9d">
    <head>Related Materials</head>
<p>Current versions of Cornell University policies can be found here: <extref href="hhttps://www.dfa.cornell.edu/policy" show="new">https://www.dfa.cornell.edu/policy</extref></p>  </relatedmaterial>
